        <owl:disjointWith rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/bea/ontologies/2026/3clasificacion_MDR_IVDR#SingleUse"/>
        <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">A powered device introduced totally or partially into the body via surgery or medical intervention (including natural orifices) and intended to remain there after the procedure.</rdfs:comment>
